<p>PatternAgents has created a new Github Site for the community development of the <b>thingSoC</b> platform.
</p>
<!-- more -->
<p><b>thingSoC</b> is a modular development platform for the Internet of Things,
that addresses many of the limitations of current product offerings;
such as automatic device discovery, automatic device configuration,
and self testing capabilities. 
</p>
<p>
<img src="{{site.url.images}}/projects/thingSoC/thingSoC.png" alt="thingSoC" title="thingSoC">
</p>
<p>
<b>thingSoC</b> is backward compatible with existing XBee format radios,<br>
(such as the Microchip "WiFly" 802.11 Wi-Fi radio shown above)<br>
but adds many new Features and capabilites that make designing<br>
your next IoT device much easier and more reliable.
</p>
<p>
